Text.string: Vault Hunter.
Good to see you.
How's the fight?
There's our Vault Hunter!
Glad you're with us, Vault Hunter.
Nice day for some ass-kickin', right?
Vault Hunter! Today's our lucky day.
Evening, Vault Hunter.
Another night, another fight, huh?
Nice Dahl gear! Not as high-tech as Atlas, but super pro.
Love that tactical Dahl gear you got.
Oooh, that's a nice Jakobs you got there. Family heirloom?
Nice gun. Is that real wood?
Hyperion! Nice. I love anything that keeps bullets off me.
Those Hyperion guns are all sharp angles!
Nice Vladof. Great what they're doing with the underbarrels, right?
Lorelei has a Vladof, YOU have a Vladof. Are Vladofs cool now?
I don't trust Tediore guns. Always feel like they're watching me.
Hey, keep an eye on that Tediore, might try and walk away.
Torgue, huh? Love that splash damage.
Is that a Torgue gun? Oh man, what does he say? “I loooove big kabooms!” Yeah, I think that's it.
Their guns have melted a ton of my friends, but I'll admit... Maliwan knows how to make 'em.
You should trade that Maliwan in for an Atlas. State of the art!
Reppin' the Atlas brand! Yeah!
How's that Atlas gun treating you? Good, right? Leave a review, it really helps us.
Wish I could go and take the fight to the bad guys!
I got patrol duty! Again. It's always patrol duty.
As a soldier, I have one hand on my gun, and one hand on my coffee at all times. “Lean, mean, and full of caffeine!”
That Lorelei is an inspiration! Bloody, brutal, and she taught me some sweet new curse words! “Ya wanker!” Classic!
This is my rifle, this is my gun! Never let go till the battle is won!
You know what's so dangerous about those Calypso Twins? They're insecure egomaniacs—that's the cause of all wars. Insecurity. That's why I've never started a war. I'm all right!
Have you tried that sandwich that has Vercuvian ham as the bread? It is... hard to eat. It's a real toothbreaker. Trust me.
Ready for some action! Not... too much action, though.
Feels good to wear crimson!
Put in a good word for me with Rhys.
Before this war, I was a nobody. Now I'm a nobody with PURPOSE!
I'm proud to be an Atlas soldier. Commander Rhys never sends us to battle on an empty stomach!
I'd give my life for Atlas. It's the only corporation that's ever tried to fix Promethea. Of course, Atlas WAS sort of responsible for Promethea's downfall, but that's ancient history. Sorta.
One day, we were just minding our business, living our lifes, and then Maliwan invaded. Bastards. But we'll get 'em!
Sanctuary is all right, but it doesn't have state-of-the-art Atlas cloaking. I feel naked up here, ya know? You get me?
Ships and cities are two of the most dangerous battle environments for a soldier. But I can't get enough of 'em!
Can't wait until the next shore leave. I'm gonna get me a big-ass sandwich!
Why do they call this ship Sanctuary? Are there, like, endangered animals in here?||—Or are WE the endangered animals? Hohhh...
This ship sort of reminds me of the big city. Crowded. Smelly. And no public restroom in sight!
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
See you 'round.
Go kick some ass.
Roger that.
See ya, Vault Hunter.
10-4, catch you on the flip.
Stay lean, mean, and full of caffeine!
Dismissed! Heh, just kidding.
Watch your ass, soldier!
Make us proud!
For Atlas!
Figures the day I get to hang out with a Vault Hunter is the day I leave my autograph book in the barracks.
I haven't been out of this armor in a month. At this point, it's less about keeping bullets out than the stink in.
Does anyone have some ammo? I used all mine and I'm sad now.
Maliwan sucks! Let's start a chant. Maliwan sucks! Maliwan sucks! Anyone? Man...
No, YOUR aim sucks, Josh!||—THAT'S what I should've said. Damn.
Crap, I farted. Hope no one can smell it through the suit...
What were my orders? What am I DOING HERE?
Seems like this war's gone on forever. Wait, which war are we in right now?
Remember when anyone in the six galaxies wasn't insane? Me neither.
I'd clean my boots, but... they're just gonna get mud on them again.
Guhh, I'm awake, I'm awake!
For Atlas! Right? Anyone?
Someone give me an order. I need an ORDER!
Tennn-hut!||—Huh. What does that mean, anyway?
Has anyone seen my sandwich? It was big with a bite out of it and mine and I wasn't done with it.
Soldier LIFE!
Bein' supportive!
Let's hear it for clapping!
Guns! Yeah!
I'm a spaceman!
Go shoot something!
Approved!
Recycled suit air is my JAM!
Do my gloves make my clapping sound weird?
[burps]
[burps]
[burps]
Wish me luck on my Atlas exam!
I forgot what we're doing, but... I'm still having fun!
Zipper's stuck and I gotta pee. Help?
Suit's kinda restrictive.
I'll take a beer if you're offering.
Feeling ignored here!
